401  static inline std::string resolution2str(RESOLUTION res) {
402  std::string output;
403  switch (res) {
404  case RESOLUTION::RESOLUTION_HD2K:
405  output = "HD2K";
406  break;
407  case RESOLUTION::RESOLUTION_HD1080:
408  output = "HD1080";
409  break;
410  case RESOLUTION::RESOLUTION_HD720:
411  output = "HD720";
412  break;
413  case RESOLUTION::RESOLUTION_VGA:
414  output = "VGA";
415  break;
416  case RESOLUTION::RESOLUTION_LAST:
417  output = "Unknown";
418  break;
419  default:
420  output = "Unknown";
421  break;
422  }
423  return output;
424  }
425 
432  static inline std::string statusCode2str(SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE state) {
433  std::string output;
434  switch (state) {
435  case SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE::SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE_NOT_STARTED:
436  output = "Self calibration: Not Started";
437  break;
438  case SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE::SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE_RUNNING:
439  output = "Self calibration: Running";
440  break;
441  case SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE::SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE_FAILED:
442  output = "Self calibration: Failed";
443  break;
444  case SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE::SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE_SUCCESS:
445  output = "Self calibration: Success";
446  break;
447  case SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE::SELF_CALIBRATION_STATE_LAST:
448  output = "Unknown";
449  break;
450  default:
451  output = "Unknown";
452  break;
453  }
454  return output;
455  }

463  static inline DEPTH_MODE str2mode(std::string mode) {
464  DEPTH_MODE output = DEPTH_MODE_PERFORMANCE;
465  if (!mode.compare("None"))
466  output = DEPTH_MODE_NONE;
467  if (!mode.compare("Performance"))
468  output = DEPTH_MODE_PERFORMANCE;
469  if (!mode.compare("Medium"))
470  output = DEPTH_MODE_MEDIUM;
471  if (!mode.compare("Quality"))
472  output = DEPTH_MODE_QUALITY;
473  return output;
474  }
475

572  static inline UNIT str2unit(std::string unit) {
573  UNIT output = UNIT_MILLIMETER;
574  if (!unit.compare("Millimeter"))
575  output = UNIT_MILLIMETER;
576  if (!unit.compare("Centimeter"))
577  output = UNIT_CENTIMETER;
578  if (!unit.compare("Meter"))
579  output = UNIT_METER;
580  if (!unit.compare("Inch"))
581  output = UNIT_INCH;
582  if (!unit.compare("Feet"))
583  output = UNIT_FOOT;
584  return output;
585  }
